## SECTION 6 FORMATTING CHECKLIST

- [ ] **Section Heading:** "SECTION 6: RESULTS AND FINDINGS" (12pt, bold, centered)
- [ ] **Finding Subheadings:** "Finding N: [Title]" (11pt, bold, left-aligned)
- [ ] **Figure References:** "Figure 6.X.X — [Type]: [Title]" with data source
- [ ] **ORIR Structure:** Clear labels or implicit structure (O in paragraph 1, R in 2, I in 3, Rec in 4)
- [ ] **Paragraph Spacing:** Single paragraph break between sections, double before new finding
- [ ] **Font:** Times New Roman, 12pt throughout
- [ ] **Spacing:** 1.5 line spacing, justified alignment
- [ ] **Quantification:** Every metric statement includes ₹, %, or #
- [ ] **Professional Tone:** Third-person, passive voice, no "I/we"
- [ ] **Page Layout:** Balanced text/visual ratio, no orphaned charts, charts integrated inline

