### ✅ ELITE (Use This)

"Slow-mover analysis identifies 23 products (26% of portfolio) with DSLS >90 days, 
collectively holding ₹176.4k inventory generating <₹2.3k monthly revenue. Carrying cost 
for these 23 SKUs (₹44.1k annually) EXCEEDS their total annual revenue (₹27.6k), 
resulting in net ₹16.5k annual loss before spoilage adjustment."

### ❌ WEAK (Avoid This)

"Some products don't sell well and are costing the business money. We should get rid 
of them to save space and money."

